{"data":[{"type":"raw_html","html":"<div class=\"para\"><span class=\"light-bold\">String Methods</span></div><div class=\"spacer-line-m\"></div><div class=\"para\">Here are some commonly used Java String methods for performing string operations.</div><div class=\"spacer-line-xl\"></div>"},{"type":"table","html":"<table class='ctable'><tr><td class='ctable-header-top-left' style='min-width:240px'>Method</td><td class='ctable-header-mid' style='min-width:240px'>Description</td><td class='ctable-header-mid'>Example</td><td class='ctable-header-top-right'>Output</td></tr><tr><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">length()</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>Returns the number of characters in the string</td><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">\"Hello\".length()</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>5</td></tr><tr><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">concat(String str)</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>Combines two strings together</td><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">\"Hello\".concat(\"World\")</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>\"HelloWorld\"</td></tr><tr><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">charAt(int index)</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>Returns character at given position (starts from 0)</td><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">\"Hello\".charAt(1)</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>'e'</td></tr><tr><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">endsWith(String suffix)</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>Checks if string ends with the specified suffix</td><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">\"Hello\".endsWith(\"lo\")</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>true</td></tr><tr><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">indexOf(String str)</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>Returns first position of substring</td><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">\"Hello\".indexOf(\"l\")</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>2</td></tr><tr><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">lastIndexOf(String str)</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>Returns last position of substring</td><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">\"Hello\".lastIndexOf(\"l\")</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>3</td></tr><tr><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">replace(char old, char new)</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>Replaces all occurrences of a character</td><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">\"Hello\".replace(\"l\", \"v\")</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>\"Hevvo\"</td></tr><tr><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">startsWith(String prefix)</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>Checks if string starts with the given prefix</td><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">\"Hello\".startsWith(\"H\")</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>true</td></tr><tr><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">toLowerCase()</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>Converts all characters to lowercase</td><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">\"Hello\".toLowerCase()</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>\"hello\"</td></tr><tr><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">toUpperCase()</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>Converts all characters to uppercase</td><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">\"Hello\".toUpperCase()</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>\"HELLO\"</td></tr><tr><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">equals(String str)</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>Checks if two strings are exactly the same</td><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">\"Java\".equals(\"java\")</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>false</td></tr><tr><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">equalsIgnoreCase(String str)</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>Compares strings ignoring case</td><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">\"Java\".equalsIgnoreCase(\"java\")</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>true</td></tr><tr><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">contains(CharSequence s)</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>Checks if the string contains the specified sequence</td><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">\"Java\".contains(\"av\")</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>true</td></tr><tr><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">substring(int begin)</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>Returns substring from index to end</td><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">\"Programming\".substring(3)</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>\"gramming\"</td></tr><tr><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">substring(int start, int end)</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>Returns part of string from start to end-1</td><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">\"Programming\".substring(0, 6)</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>\"Progra\"</td></tr><tr><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">trim()</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>Removes leading and trailing spaces</td><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">\"  Hello  \".trim()</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>\"Hello\"</td></tr><tr><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">isEmpty()</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>Checks if the string has 0 characters</td><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">\"\".isEmpty()</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>true</td></tr><tr><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">split(String regex)</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>Splits string into array using the given delimiter</td><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">\"a,b,c\".split(\",\")</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>[\"a\", \"b\", \"c\"]</td></tr><tr><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">valueOf(anyType)</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>Converts any data type to string</td><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">String.valueOf(123)</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>\"123\"</td></tr><tr><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">compareTo(String str)</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>Compares two strings lexicographically</td><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">\"apple\".compareTo(\"banana\")</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>Negative number</td></tr><tr><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">matches(String regex)</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>Returns true if the string matches the regex pattern</td><td class='ctable-data'><span class=\"code-highlight\">\"12345\".matches(\"\\\\\\\\d+\")</span></td><td class='ctable-data'>true</td></tr></table>"},{"type":"raw_html","html":"<div class=\"spacer-line-l\"></div><div class=\"para\">There are many more methods in the String class. You can find them <span class=\"link-text-with-open-in\" onclick=\"openInNewTab('https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/lang/String.html')\"><span class=\"link-text\">here</span><span class=\"open-in-new-tab-icon\"></span></span></div><div class=\"spacer-line-xl\"></div><div class=\"para\"><span class=\"light-bold\">Coding Tips</span></div><div class=\"para\">In Java, String is immutable: Once created, it canâ€™t be changed. Every method that \"modifies\" a string actually returns a new string.</div><div class=\"para\">Indexes start from 0: <span class=\"code-highlight\">\"Hello\".charAt(0)</span> is 'H'.</div><div class=\"para\">Use <span class=\"code-highlight\">.equals()</span> to compare strings, not <span class=\"code-highlight\">==</span>, because <span class=\"code-highlight\">==</span> checks memory address, not value.</div><div class=\"spacer-line-xl\"></div><div class=\"para\"><span class=\"light-bold\">Reference</span></div>"},{"type":"spacer","size":"4"},{"type":"links","links":[{"displayText":"Java - String Class - tutorialspoint.com","link":"https://www.tutorialspoint.com/java/java_strings.htm"},{"displayText":"Java Demo String And String Methods","link":"https://github.com/VaibhavMojidra/Java---Demo-String-And-String-Methods"},{"displayText":"Java - String Class - docs.oracle.com","link":"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/lang/String.html"}]}],"isCopyAllowed":false,"copyText":"","isReadAllowed":false,"readOutText":"","readoutReplace":[]}